{"tid":146875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯法院內selfie涉違法　警方：已完成調查不檢控","createTime":"2017-03-07T12:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T16:23:01.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"047ef3cd02c6765e0221d2db446d7753d6644315","tid":146875,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170307/large/1488888729_123b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F1488888729_123b.jpg&h=7e5dd733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港律師會前會長何君堯去年4月在其個人facebook，上載一張於法庭外、但在法院範圍內的selfie自拍照，涉嫌知法犯法，引起公眾譁然。警察公共關係科今日回覆本報查詢時表示，警方已完成調查，經徵詢法律意見後沒有對任何人作出檢控，並已於今年1月通知報案人有關調查結果。至於沒有作出檢控的原因，警方則未有解釋。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯去年4月28日在facebook上載涉案庭外自拍照，圖片說明寫上「在28庭內，未見成功，先見其母！培叔忍耐呀！」相信是攝於高院大樓內的第28庭門外，有關新界原居民「套丁案」被裁定串謀詐騙罪成的丁屋發展商李欽培日前申請保釋等候上訴案件。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯事後發聲明指自己上載該照片「絕無任何惡意或對法庭不敬的含意」，力撐有關照片並沒有構成違法成份。<br />\n<br />\n惟司法機構發言人即日表示，已經將有關事件轉交警方跟進和處理，並謂根據《簡易程序治罪條例》，除非獲得特別許可，任何人士不得在法庭或舉行聆訊的建築物範圍內拍攝。一般而言，法庭內不可以攝影。至於法庭外的公眾等候區，只有在獲得特別許可下，例如在舉行委任儀式後，才可以在該處攝影。警方亦回應指，中區警署當日傍晚6時35分接獲一名女職員報案，指懷疑有人在其位於中區金鐘道的法院內拍照。案件列作求警協助，交由中區警區人員跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科當值新聞主任今日回覆本報查詢時表示：「中區警署於二○一六年四月二十八日接獲一名女職員報案，指懷疑有人在其位於中區金鐘道的法院內拍照。警方已完成調查，經徵詢法律意見後沒有對任何人作出檢控。警方已於今年一月通知報案人有關調查結果。」據了解，法律意見來自律政司。"},{"pid":"5f9f186684f370822833bb5ecd173be7a1b1b0e4","tid":146875,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:46:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170307&amp;guid=56397826&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170307%26guid%3D56397826%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=dbb3b019\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170307%26guid%3D56397826%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=44f76c2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170307&amp;guid=56397826&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"8e93b571cbf4613b60f57ecb20b1b99a7daa2fe4","tid":146875,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b31c55a02006090f7328bdad50b2e420bead41","tid":146875,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be98b18befccd943e5eb10d49084f663425f0e0","tid":146875,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:51:36.000Z","msg":"」據了解，法律意見來自律政司。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為佢西環人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ceae0f36c674907a8e8bd9286c8af9c4921b387","tid":146875,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b54fddfc623f6d7329e121ee43bb618b5ff23c9","tid":146875,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:05:09.000Z","msg":"都估到啦。親共既點會告"},{"pid":"19caaec70669d81280784e85e6d82f6736cbbd5c","tid":146875,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都估到啦。親共既點會告</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370f4117a0a0cba64140f13493b109c99d2c9f30","tid":146875,"uid":58893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:08:22.000Z","msg":"有捐錢比黑警咪冇事"},{"pid":"f65328e9303050cc237aa3866bd6c0aaeabd805d","tid":146875,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13: